2:T90d,[{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Place","name":"West Village","description":"The West Village is perhaps Manhattan's most coveted residential neighborhood — a maze of pre-grid streets lined with Federal townhouses, flowering window boxes, and restaurants that have maintained t","url":"https://withpush.co/neighborhoods/west-village","geo":{"@type":"GeoCoordinates","latitude":40.7348,"longitude":-74.006},"address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"West Village","addressRegion":"NY","addressCountry":"US"},"containedInPlace":{"@type":"City","name":"New York City"}},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How does Push work in West Village?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Push connects local creators with merchants in West Village, Manhattan. Creators visit participating businesses, scan a QR code to verify their visit, then publish content. Merchants pay only for verified foot traffic — no guessing required."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How many campaigns are active in West Village right now?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"West Village currently has 19 active creator campaigns across 24 merchants, with 87 creators operating in this neighborhood."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What is the average campaign payout in West Village?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The average campaign payout in West Village is $72 per verified visit. Total verified visits in this neighborhood have reached 2,891."}}]},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"ItemList","name":"Featured Merchants in West Village","numberOfItems":3,"itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"item":{"@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"Via Carota","address":"51 Grove St, New York, NY 10014","description":"Food & Drink business in West Village with 1 active Push campaign."}},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"item":{"@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"Murray's Cheese","address":"254 Bleecker St, New York, NY 10014","description":"Specialty Food business in West Village with 2 active Push campaigns."}},{"@type":"ListItem","position":3,"item":{"@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"Buvette","address":"42 Grove St, New York, NY 10014","description":"Food & Drink business in West Village with 1 active Push campaign."}}]}]4:T43c,The West Village is perhaps Manhattan's most coveted residential neighborhood — a maze of pre-grid streets lined with Federal townhouses, flowering window boxes, and restaurants that have maintained their reputation for decades without resorting to hype. Hudson Street and Bleecker Street anchor a dining scene that prioritizes hospitality over spectacle: old-school Italian red sauce joints, intimate wine bars, cheese shops that have been here longer than most of their customers. Push operates here at moderate density — the neighborhood's merchant community is selective about creator partnerships, preferring smaller, highly engaged creators over mass-reach accounts. Campaign briefs here emphasize authenticity and neighborhood fit. The average campaign payout in the West Village is among Push's highest: merchants budget for quality because their customers expect it. Creators who perform best in this neighborhood have a genuine connection to the area — they've eaten at these restaurants, they know the bartenders, their content reads as local rather than promotional.0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","main",null,{"className":"nh-page","children":[["$","section",null,{"className":"nhd-hero","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container nhd-hero-inner","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"nhd-breadcrumb","aria-label":"Breadcrumb","children":[["$","$L3",null,{"href":"/","children":"Push"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"nhd-breadcrumb-sep","children":"/"}],["$","$L3",null,{"href":"/neighborhoods","children":"Neighborhoods"}],["$","span",null,{"c